download through download.py the data semseg.v2.json and the labels.instance.annotated.v2.ply:
    - the first one is the .ply of the scene
    - the second one rapresents a set of feature of all the objects in the scene:
        - objectId
        - id
        - partId
        - index 
        - dominantNormal
        - obb
        - centroid
        - normalizedAxes
        - segments
        - label (bed, armchair, wall, floor)

run the transform_ply.py under utils to generate labels.instances.align.annotated.v2.ply:
    